title: Disables fixed-size widgets on Android 3.0+
message:
Disables fixed-size widgets on Android 3.0+

Upon first start of WidgetDemo (which should happen when the user first
installs the widgets) the fixed / resizable widgets will be enabled /
disabled based on the platform's version. That way Android 3.0+ users
don't see multiple sizes of widgets.

title: Adds support for larger widgets
message:
Adds support for larger widgets

This adds 3x and 4x sizes of the widget.
